E-Commerce Sales Application Documentation
1. Project Overview
Project Name
Sacy Shoes E-Commerce Platform
Purpose
An online sales platform that allows customers to browse products, add items to a cart, pay online using Mobile Money and other payment methods through Paystack, track orders, and manage their accounts.
The system will also provide an administrative dashboard for managing products, orders, customers, payments, and reports.
 
2. Technology Stack
Backend
•	Laravel 12 
•	PHP 8.3+ 
•	MySQL 8 
Frontend
•	Laravel Blade 
•	Tailwind CSS 
•	Alpine.js 
Payment Gateway
•	Paystack 
Hosting
•	cPanel Hosting (initially) 
•	VPS (future scaling) 
